{"openapi":"3.0.1","info":{"title":"智途平台 API","description":"智途云平台 - 高校产教融合智能服务平台接口文档","version":"v1.0.0"},"servers":[{"url":"http://localhost:8888","description":"API Gateway"}],"security":[{"BearerAuth":[]}],"tags":[{"name":"认证管理","description":"用户认证、登录、Token 管理相关接口"}],"paths":{"/api/auth/v1/token/refresh":{"post":{"tags":["认证管理"],"summary":"${api.auth.refresh.summary}","description":"${api.auth.refresh.description}\n\n**测试前置条件：**\n- 必须先通过 /login 接口获取有效的 refreshToken\n- refreshToken 必须未过期且未被撤销\n- 用户账号必须仍然有效（未被删除或禁用）\n\n**数据依赖：**\n- 依赖 Redis 中存储的 refreshToken\n- 依赖 sys_user 表中的用户状态","operationId":"refresh","requestBody":{"description":"刷新令牌请求信息","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/RefreshTokenRequest"},"examples":{"刷新令牌":{"summary":"使用刷新令牌获取新的访问令牌","description":"刷新令牌","value":{"refreshToken":"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiIxMjM0NTY3ODkwIiwibmFtZSI6IkpvaG4gRG9lIiwiaWF0IjoxNTE2MjM5MDIyfQ.SflKxwRJSMeKKF2QT4fwpMeJf36POk6yJV_adQssw5c"}}}}},"required":true},"responses":{"500":{"description":"${api.auth.login.response.500}","content":{"application/json":{"example":{"code":500,"message":"服务器内部错误","data":null}}}},"404":{"description":"Not Found","content":{"*/*":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/ResultVoid"}}}},"401":{"description":"${api.auth.refresh.response.401}","content":{"application/json":{"examples":{"刷新令牌无效":{"description":"刷新令牌无效","value":{"code":1006,"message":"Refresh Token 无效或已过期","data":null}},"Token已过期":{"description":"Token已过期","value":{"code":1005,"message":"Token 已过期","data":null}}}}}},"403":{"description":"Forbidden","content":{"*/*":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/ResultVoid"}}}},"400":{"description":"${api.auth.login.response.400}","content":{"application/json":{"example":{"code":422,"message":"参数校验失败","data":null}}}},"200":{"description":"${api.auth.refresh.response.200}","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/Result"}}}}}}},"/api/auth/v1/logout":{"post":{"tags":["认证管理"],"summary":"${api.auth.logout.summary}","description":"${api.auth.logout.description}\n\n**测试前置条件：**\n- 用户必须已登录并持有有效的 JWT token\n- Authorization header 格式：Bearer {token}\n\n**数据依赖：**\n- 依赖 Redis 中存储的 token 和 refreshToken\n- 清除操作不依赖数据库，仅清除缓存","operationId":"logout","parameters":[{"name":"Authorization","in":"header","description":"${api.auth.logout.param.authorization}","required":false,"schema":{"type":"string"}}],"requestBody":{"content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/RefreshTokenRequest"}}}},"responses":{"500":{"description":"${api.auth.login.response.500}","content":{"application/json":{"example":{"code":500,"message":"服务器内部错误","data":null}}}},"404":{"description":"Not Found","content":{"*/*":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/ResultVoid"}}}},"401":{"description":"${api.auth.logout.response.401}","content":{"application/json":{"examples":{"Token无效":{"description":"Token无效","value":{"code":1004,"message":"Token 无效","data":null}},"Token已过期":{"description":"Token已过期","value":{"code":1005,"message":"Token 已过期","data":null}}}}}},"403":{"description":"Forbidden","content":{"*/*":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/ResultVoid"}}}},"400":{"description":"Bad Request","content":{"*/*":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/ResultVoid"}}}},"200":{"description":"${api.auth.logout.response.200}","content":{"application/json":{"example":{"code":200,"message":"操作成功","data":null}}}}}}},"/api/auth/v1/login":{"post":{"tags":["认证管理"],"summary":"${api.auth.login.summary}","description":"${api.auth.login.description}\n\n**测试前置条件：**\n- 用户账号必须已在对应租户的用户表中存在\n- 租户（tenant）必须已创建且状态为启用\n- 用户状态必须为正常（status=1），非锁定或注销状态\n\n**数据依赖：**\n- 依赖 sys_user 表中的用户记录\n- 依赖 sys_tenant 表中的租户记录\n- 密码需使用 BCrypt 加密存储","operationId":"login","requestBody":{"description":"登录请求信息","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/LoginRequest"},"examples":{"学生登录":{"summary":"学生角色登录示例","description":"学生登录","value":{"role":"student","username":"zhangsan","password":"password123"}},"企业登录":{"summary":"企业角色登录示例","description":"企业登录","value":{"role":"enterprise","username":"company_hr","password":"password123"}},"高校登录":{"summary":"高校角色登录示例","description":"高校登录","value":{"role":"college","username":"teacher_wang","password":"password123"}},"平台管理员登录":{"summary":"平台管理员登录示例","description":"平台管理员登录","value":{"role":"platform","username":"admin","password":"admin123"}},"边界值-最短用户名":{"summary":"最短用户名（3个字符）","description":"边界值-最短用户名","value":{"role":"student","username":"abc","password":"pass123"}},"边界值-最长用户名":{"summary":"最长用户名（50个字符）","description":"边界值-最长用户名","value":{"role":"student","username":"abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz1234567890abcdefghijklmn","password":"password123"}},"特殊字符-中文用户名":{"summary":"包含中文字符的用户名","description":"特殊字符-中文用户名","value":{"role":"student","username":"张三_student","password":"密码123"}},"特殊字符-邮箱格式":{"summary":"邮箱格式的用户名","description":"特殊字符-邮箱格式","value":{"role":"enterprise","username":"user@example.com","password":"P@ssw0rd!"}},"特殊字符-下划线和数字":{"summary":"包含下划线和数字的用户名","description":"特殊字符-下划线和数字","value":{"role":"college","username":"user_123_test","password":"Test@2024"}},"边界值-空字符串测试":{"summary":"空字符串（应该失败）","description":"边界值-空字符串测试","value":{"role":"","username":"","password":""}}}}},"required":true},"responses":{"500":{"description":"${api.auth.login.response.500}","content":{"application/json":{"example":{"code":500,"message":"服务器内部错误","data":null}}}},"404":{"description":"Not Found","content":{"*/*":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/ResultVoid"}}}},"401":{"description":"${api.auth.login.response.401}","content":{"application/json":{"examples":{"用户不存在":{"description":"用户不存在","value":{"code":1001,"message":"用户不存在","data":null}},"密码错误":{"description":"密码错误","value":{"code":1002,"message":"密码错误","data":null}},"账号已被禁用":{"description":"账号已被禁用","value":{"code":1003,"message":"账号已被禁用","data":null}},"租户不存在":{"description":"租户不存在","value":{"code":1007,"message":"租户不存在","data":null}},"租户已被禁用":{"description":"租户已被禁用","value":{"code":1008,"message":"租户已被禁用","data":null}}}}}},"403":{"description":"Forbidden","content":{"*/*":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/ResultVoid"}}}},"400":{"description":"${api.auth.login.response.400}","content":{"application/json":{"example":{"code":422,"message":"参数校验失败","data":null}}}},"200":{"description":"${api.auth.login.response.200}","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/Result"}}}}}}}},"components":{"schemas":{"ResultVoid":{"required":["code","message"],"type":"object","properties":{"code":{"type":"integer","description":"响应状态码，200表示成功","format":"int32","example":200},"message":{"type":"string","description":"响应消息","example":"操作成功"},"data":{"type":"object","description":"响应数据"}},"description":"统一响应体"},"RefreshTokenRequest":{"required":["refreshToken"],"type":"object","properties":{"refreshToken":{"type":"string","description":"刷新令牌","example":"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..."}},"description":"${api.auth.logout.param.request}"},"Result":{"required":["code","message"],"type":"object","properties":{"code":{"type":"integer","description":"响应状态码，200表示成功","format":"int32","example":200},"message":{"type":"string","description":"响应消息","example":"操作成功"},"data":{"type":"object","description":"响应数据"}},"description":"统一响应体"},"LoginRequest":{"required":["password","role","username"],"type":"object","properties":{"role":{"type":"string","description":"用户角色","example":"student","enum":["student","enterprise","college","platform"]},"loginType":{"type":"string","description":"登录类型（预留）","example":"password","enum":["password","phone"]},"username":{"maxLength":50,"minLength":3,"type":"string","description":"用户名","example":"zhangsan"},"password":{"maxLength":128,"minLength":6,"type":"string","description":"密码","example":"password123"}},"description":"登录请求信息"}},"securitySchemes":{"BearerAuth":{"type":"http","name":"BearerAuth","scheme":"bearer","bearerFormat":"JWT"}}}}